    <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="display-6">About Us</h2>
    </div>

    <p>
        Welcome to <b>InterRegister</b>, your trusted partner in navigating the journey towards a fulfilling and successful career. We understand that choosing the right path in life can be both exciting and daunting, and that's why we're here to guide you every step of the way.
    </p>

    <div>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <b>Our Mission:</b>
                <p>
                    At InternRegister, our mission is to empower individuals to make informed decisions about their careers and to help them embark on a journey that aligns with their passions, skills, and aspirations. We believe that everyone deserves a fulfilling and rewarding career, and we are committed to providing the guidance and resources needed to achieve that goal.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li>
                <b>Our Approach:</b>
                <p>
                    Our approach to career counseling is personalized and holistic. We understand that each individual is unique, and we tailor our services to meet your specific needs and goals. Whether you're a recent graduate exploring your options, a mid-career professional seeking a change, or someone looking to re-enter the workforce, we have the expertise to support you.
                </p>
            </li>

            <li>
                <b>What We Offer:</b>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        Personalized Career Assessments: Our career counselors work closely with you to assess your interests, strengths, and values. Through a series of assessments and discussions, we help you gain clarity about your career goals.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Expert Guidance: Our team of experienced career counselors and industry experts provide you with valuable insights into various career options, industry trends, and job market demands.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Resume and Interview Preparation: We offer assistance in creating a standout resume and preparing for interviews, equipping you with the skills needed to impress potential employers.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Job Search Strategies: We provide guidance on effective job search strategies, networking, and online presence optimization to increase your chances of finding the right job.

                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Skill Development: If you need to acquire new skills or enhance existing ones, we offer recommendations for relevant courses and training programs.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Internship Placement: For students and recent graduates, we assist in finding internship opportunities that align with your career aspirations.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Career Workshops and Webinars: We host informative workshops and webinars on a wide range of career-related topics to keep you informed and motivated.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>

            <li>
                <b>Why Choose Us:</b>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Experienced Team: Our team of career counselors and industry experts bring years of experience and insights to the table.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Personalized Approach: We treat each client as an individual with unique goals and needs, ensuring tailored guidance.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Up-to-Date Knowledge: We stay current with industry trends and job market dynamics to provide you with the most relevant advice.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Success Stories: Many individuals have successfully launched their careers with our guidance. Check out our success stories to see the impact we've had.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li>
